      "recommendation": "string — specific action to take",
      "priority": "low | medium | high",
      "requires_reiteration": false
    }
  ],
  "should_reiterate": false
}

Return between 3 and 8 improvement recommendations sorted by priority (high first).
Be honest — do not inflate scores. A score of 60-75 is typical for a first pass.
